<DocsLayout
  title="Search"
  description="SignalPaper uses Pagefind to provide static search across posts and projects."
>
  <h2>How it works</h2>
  <p>The build command runs Astro first, then Pagefind. Pagefind reads the generated static pages and creates the search index inside <code>dist/pagefind</code>.</p>

  <h2>Search scope</h2>
  <p>The default search modal covers public post and project detail pages. Results are filtered by the current page language.</p>

  <h2>Local testing</h2>
  <p>Use <code>npm run build</code> and <code>npm run preview</code> when testing search. Search is not expected to work in the same way during raw development mode.</p>
</DocsLayout>

